{"tid":332953,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019]Marvel神力女超人 - Captain Marvel 細節公開","createTime":"2017-07-23T11:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T13:14:23.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71d9de893b545caeb20e9d0a8bb7345a4ec235fe","tid":332953,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"Info.: The Avengers-復仇者聯盟(香港粉絲團)<br />\n<br />\n【SDCC 2017 消息】<br />\n更多《Marvel 隊長》的細節公開<br />\n在剛結束的MARVEL發佈會中，雖然沒有新片名公佈，但一口氣發放了不少未來電影的更多詳情。其中將於2019年上映的《Marvel 隊長》（Captain Marvel，暫譯）亦有不少資料公佈。<br />\n首先電影將會設定於90年代，似乎能夠為MCU的背景加添更多故事。而森姆積遜（Samuel L. Jackson）將會回歸飾演費局長（Nick Fury），回到那時他還未戴上眼罩，以雙目示人。<br />\n此外，Marvel隊長面對的敵人將會是漫畫的反派外星種族－Skrulls，他們有隨意變成不少生物或死物外表的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.comicbookmovie.com/captain_marvel/brie-larsons-captain-marvel-battles-the-skrulls-in-first-movie-concept-art-nick-fury-confirmed-a152755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comicbookmovie.com%2Fcaptain_marvel%2Fbrie-larsons-captain-marvel-battles-the-skrulls-in-first-movie-concept-art-nick-fury-confirmed-a152755&d=WBxgLKRbSoXNuYZPkEN3uCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b8299e39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.comicbookmovie.com/captain_marvel/brie-larsons-captain-marvel-battles-the-skrulls-in-first-movie-concept-art-nick-fury-confirmed-a152755</a>"},{"pid":"b46c318f81f31ccf7e6075108aa10ade2b104d49","tid":332953,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s9.postimg.org/hojvzfx0v/DFYado5_VYAAZ3iv-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs9.postimg.org%2Fhojvzfx0v%2FDFYado5_VYAAZ3iv-1.jpg&h=c2d1fbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFYaYtxUAAQOej9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFYaYtxUAAQOej9.jpg&h=95fd10e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFYamuMV0AAqmqd.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFYamuMV0AAqmqd.jpg%3Aorig&h=cc58a3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFYado5VYAAZ3iv.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFYado5VYAAZ3iv.jpg%3Aorig&h=7e38469c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d905394238f016eae53224f63ff00ad5f822c87","tid":332953,"uid":44775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"經期隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ad54241c5cafb14a1e205256cfb270cd6ea9f9","tid":332953,"uid":27269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"終於等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}